            <p:rationale>If applications have no knowledge of each other's data model, then the unaffected application does not need to be amended during replacement of one application. In general, applications are more maintainable if they have no knowledge of the data models of other applications.</p:rationale>
            <p:implications>Use is made of a canonical model given in communication between applications. Translations between applications take place in the integration infrastructure. When replacing an integration applications do not need to be adjusted.</p:implications>
